## The "Operational Math" (AI Expenses)
Running an automation machine isn't free. You should ensure Matt covers these **Direct Costs**:
*   **LLM Tokens (OpenAI/Claude):** Every message your WhatsApp Stylist sends or every script your Billy Mays bot writes costs a few cents. At scale, this can hit $20–$100/mo.
*   **API Subscriptions:** Tools like **ElevenLabs** (Credit based) and potentially **Browse.ai** or **Apify** for scale scraping.
*   **Social Posting Tools:** If you use an auto-scheduler like Buffer or HeyOrca.

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **The Deal:** You provide the "Brain" (n8n workflows), Matt provides the "Fuel" (API keys and billing).

