## Legal & Liability (The "Gotchas")
*   **AI Content Liability:** If your Billy Mays bot makes a medical claim (e.g., "This cures alopecia"), the brand is liable. Matt must approve the "System Prompts" for all bots.
*   **Data Privacy (WhatsApp):** Since we are routing customer hair photos and names through AI, ensure Matt’s TOS covers "Third party data processing for customer support."
*   **Tracking Transparency:** Ensure your 20% tracking link logic is transparent inside his Shopify so there are no "commission disputes" later.

